{"id":1112,"date":"2018-12-27T16:12:52","date_gmt":"2018-12-27T09:12:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/?p=1112"},"modified":"2018-12-27T16:12:52","modified_gmt":"2018-12-27T09:12:52","slug":"phong-ngu-co-2-cua-ra-vao-xet-theo-phong-thuy-la-tot-hay-xau","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/phong-ngu-co-2-cua-ra-vao-xet-theo-phong-thuy-la-tot-hay-xau","title":{"rendered":"Ph\u00f2ng Ng\u1ee7 C\u00f3 2 C\u1eeda Ra V\u00e0o &#8211; X\u00e9t theo phong th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t hay x\u1ea5u?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phong th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y b\u1eb1ng m\u1eaft th\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 phong th\u1ee7y ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eb7p v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 chung m\u1ed9t th\u1eafc m\u1eafc l\u00e0 trong ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang \u1edf, <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/phong-ngu-co-2-cua-ra-vao-xet-theo-phong-thuy-la-tot-hay-xau\"><em><strong>ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/span>, x\u00e9t theo phong th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t hay x\u1ea5u? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng<strong> Thietkethicongdn.com<\/strong> \u0111i t\u00ecm c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"Nhu_the_nao_la_phong_ngu_co_2_cua_ra_vao\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o?<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1113 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/Ph\u00f2ng-Ng\u1ee7-C\u00f3-2-C\u1eeda-Ra-V\u00e0o-X\u00e9t-theo-phong-th\u1ee7y-l\u00e0-t\u1ed1t-hay-x\u1ea5u.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" \/><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o l\u00e0 ph\u1ecfng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda ng\u0103n c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng gian trong ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i ph\u00f2ng. Ki\u1ec3u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1ecd nh\u1ecf c\u00f3 ban c\u00f4ng (M\u1ed9t c\u1eeda t\u1eeb h\u00e0nh lang \u0111i v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng, m\u1ed9t c\u1eeda t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng ra ban c\u00f4ng).<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eeda th\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 t\u1eafm th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o. V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, nh\u00e0 t\u1eafm hay nh\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i ph\u00f2ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o th\u00f4ng nhau g\u00e2y ra t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i kh\u00f4n l\u01b0\u1eddng<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1117 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/Ph\u00f2ng-Ng\u1ee7-C\u00f3-2-C\u1eeda-Ra-V\u00e0o-X\u00e9t-theo-phong-th\u1ee7y-l\u00e0-t\u1ed1t-hay-x\u1ea5u4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t phong th\u1ee7y<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Trong phong th\u1ee7y t\u1eeb x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn nay, c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 l\u00e0 con m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0, c\u00f2n c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed l\u00e0 c\u00e1i mi\u1ebfng. Do v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nhau s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf &#8220;\u0110\u1ea5u kh\u1ea9u&#8221;.<\/li>\n<li>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng xung \u0111\u1ed9t li\u00ean mi\u00ean, lu\u00f4n b\u1ea5t h\u00f2a t\u1eeb suy ngh\u0129 ra \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1eddi n\u00f3i. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng th\u00ec s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n c\u0169ng g\u00e2y ra c\u1ea3nh chia ly.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nhau s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t tho\u00e1ng kh\u00ed, t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e1t m\u1ebb v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1i g\u00ec qu\u00e1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu gi\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u1eefa 2 c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda n\u00e0y th\u00ec ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m h\u00e0n kh\u00ed m\u00e0 sinh b\u1ec7nh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t hai c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nhau khi\u1ebfn c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u00f4ng k\u00e9m sang v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"Phong_ngu_co_hai_cua_ra_vao_nen_bo_tri_the_nao_cho_hop_ly\"><strong>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o n\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho h\u1ee3p l\u00fd?<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t 2 c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nhau.<\/li>\n<li>N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd th\u1ea5y c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec n\u00ean di chuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1eeda l\u1ec7ch \u0111i c\u00e0ng xa c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<\/li>\n<li>Bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng r\u00e8m d\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea5m b\u00ecnh phong phong th\u1ee7y \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafn ngang gi\u1eefa 2 c\u1eeda. Gi\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa 2 c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc th\u1ee9 hai:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>C\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng v\u1edbi c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh.<\/li>\n<li>Theo quan ni\u1ec7m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ri\u00eang t\u01b0. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o b\u00ean trong. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bi\u1ec3u th\u1ecb cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c d\u00f2m ng\u00f3 v\u00e0 can thi\u1ec7p.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc th\u1ee9 ba:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1116 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/Ph\u00f2ng-Ng\u1ee7-C\u00f3-2-C\u1eeda-Ra-V\u00e0o-X\u00e9t-theo-phong-th\u1ee7y-l\u00e0-t\u1ed1t-hay-x\u1ea5u2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"438\" \/><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ebfu th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7.<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ec3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ebfu th\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng v\u1eadn kh\u00ed t\u1ed1t trong ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea3y ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ra ngo\u00e0i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n cho r\u1eb1ng n\u00f3 d\u1eabn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ma qu\u1ef7 v\u00e0 \u00e2m kh\u00ed v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote><p><em>&gt;&gt;&gt; XEM TH\u00caM\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/nen-hay-khong-nen-dat-guong-doi-dien-cua-ra-vao\"><strong>N\u00ean hay kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t g\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u1eeda ra v\u00e0o?<\/strong><\/a><\/span><\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&#8211; Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc th\u1ee9 t\u01b0:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eeda nh\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh &#8211; c\u1eeda nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp &#8211; nh\u00e0 kho.<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a nh\u1eefng kh\u00ed kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t cho gia ch\u1ee7. N\u00ean khi \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng kh\u00ed \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 t\u00e0i v\u1eadn.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&#8211; Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc th\u1ee9 n\u0103m:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n g\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7.<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n gi\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ee7 khi\u00ean c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ea5t an, d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y b\u1ec7nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf trong ph\u00f2ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Phong th\u1ee7y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y b\u1eb1ng m\u1eaft th\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 phong th\u1ee7y ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eb7p v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 chung m\u1ed9t th\u1eafc m\u1eafc l\u00e0 trong ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang \u1edf, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 2 c\u1eeda ra&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1113,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1112"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1112"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1112\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1119,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1112\/revisions\/1119"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1113"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1112"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1112"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1112"}],"c